Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.model

Class Event

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.model.Event
public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
Immutable class representing an event on the board. It can be either a MOVE or BUILD type of event. Events are used by IslandBoard to check if a move is possible according to other god card's rules or to check if a player has won.
